About this item

  • 2.4GHz Wi-Fi Compatible – Connects to 2.4GHz networks of single-, dual- and tri-band routers through effortless pairing options for use with the latest home Wi-Fi equipment.
  • Confident Installation – QuickFit design features reduced housing depth & eliminated break-off tabs. SimpleWire technology offers patented auto-detecting line/load terminals & off-set ground ports. Interchangeable paddles match existing décor. White is included with other colors available.
  • Easy-to-Use App – UltraPro app available on the Apple App Store & on Google Play simplifies network connection. Compatible with Amazon Alexa and Google Assistant. No hub required. Alerts & do-not-disturb function allow personalized monitoring.
  • Simple Setup – ON/OFF operation & full-range dimming creates the perfect lighting for every room. Schedules & automations support full customization based on weather, location & more. Organize devices by rooms & homes to control locations from one app.
  • Multi-Switch Capable – Single-pole & 3-way configurations. Can be used with standard 3-way switches for ON/OFF operation or up to 4 UltraPro, Enbrighten & JascoPro Series add-on switches to keep all functions of the smart device from every location.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.

Amazon Customer
5 out of 5 stars
Great Switch! Works Exactly as it Should!
I purchased this switch to be able to automate our back porch lights and connect them to the Ring doorbell motion sensor on the back porch so that at nighttime, when the motion sensor (or doorbell button) is tripped, the back porch lights will automatically turn on and remain on for 5 minutes. I was going to do this with a smart bulb, but my wife was adamant about wanting to retain manual control of the light as well, so this was the perfect solution! My initial switch purchased was an Eva Logik; however, it no longer supports Samsung Smartthings, which is the only app I can use to do the above programming. This switch does support Smartthings, and it works perfectly! It does state in the app that the WiFi signal is low, but that's because it's behind a metal cover plate - despite this, I've not had a single issue with it activating remotely in the last 2 months. I like that you can change how the LED in the switch works - by default, the switch illiminates in the ON position, but I was easily able to change it to illuminate in the OFF position in the app, as that works best in this particular scenario. NOTE: I painted the switch bezel black to match the other switches on the plate - it came with a white bezel. I cannot find a smart toggle switch in this design that has a bezel other than white. Regardless, this switch does the job perfectly! Highly recommended!

    5.0 out of 5 stars Good value for the product
    Reviewed in the United States on March 29, 2023
    Size: 1 PackStyle: Toggle DimmerVerified Purchase
    The UltraPro Wi-Fi Smart Dimmer, 2.4GHz Wi-Fi, QuickFit & SimpleWire, 3 Way Dimmer is an excellent product. It was a good value to purchase. In fact, the Wi-Fi controlled dimmer is about the same price as an LED dimmer that is not controllable. Easy to install for most untrained individuals and functions as advertised. We don't like to leave our front porch lights on when we leave the house and know we won't return until evening. One, it's a waste of electricity and two, it indicates to persons with possible nefarious intent that nobody may be home. We also don't like to return home to a dark front door. People shouldn't be paranoid but they should be aware. This remote dimmer allows us to turn on our porch lights at dusk from our cell phone using mobile data. I had some difficulty getting the unit to sync to our Wi-Fi signal after it was wired until I chose to do such manually. I tried three times to perform a sync using the automatic process to no avail. Once it synced with our Wi-Fi, it is controllable by my cell phone. It performs a full range of dimming of all lamp types, Incandescent, Compact Fluorescent and LED. The line and load contacts are interchangeable so you don't even have to necessarily know which conductor is which except for the neutral and ground which are readily identified by the color of the jacket of the wire or no jacket which denotes a ground wire. That's an excellent feature for novice wiring individuals as most other dimmers, if you wire them backwards, it could damage the dimmer. In the very least, it will not function. That problem is eliminated with this device. I would strongly encourage that this device be installed with the circuit de-energized so as not to damage the unit or harm the installer. I would also like to point out that you should not install the wall plate until you have completed syncing the unit to your smart phones. It is also compatible with Alexa and a few other systems. I ended up removing the wall plate after I got the switch wired and into the wall as you need access to the front of the unit in order to perform a sync. Overall, we are very pleased with the product. Thank you.
